<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/analytics') %>

        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>開発中 | 株式投資学習ロードマップ</title>
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
        <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

        <style>
            body {
                margin: 0;
                font-family: sans-serif;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
                min-height: 100vh;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .container {
                text-align: center;
                max-width: 600px;
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .development-card {
                background: white;
                border-radius: 20px;
                padding: 3rem 2rem;
                box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            }

            .development-icon {
                font-size: 4rem;
                color: #f59e0b;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
                animation: bounce 2s infinite;
            }

            @keyframes bounce {

                0%,
                20%,
                50%,
                80%,
                100% {
                    transform: translateY(0);
                }

                40% {
                    transform: translateY(-10px);
                }

                60% {
                    transform: translateY(-5px);
                }
            }

            .development-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #1e40af;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            .development-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                color: #64748b;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .development-description {
                font-size: 1rem;
                color: #64748b;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .back-button {
                display: inline-block;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
                color: white;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                border-radius: 25px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: 600;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
            }

            .back-button:hover {
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.4);
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .progress-indicator {
                background: #f1f5f9;
                border-radius: 10px;
                padding: 1rem;
                margin: 2rem 0;
            }

            .progress-bar {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
                height: 8px;
                border-radius: 4px;
                width: 60%;
                margin: 0 auto;
                position: relative;
                overflow: hidden;
            }

            .progress-bar::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                height: 100%;
                width: 100%;
                background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), transparent);
                animation: shimmer 2s infinite;
            }

            @keyframes shimmer {
                0% {
                    transform: translateX(-100%);
                }

                100% {
                    transform: translateX(100%);
                }
            }

            .progress-text {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                color: #64748b;
                margin-top: 0.5rem;
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .development-card {
                    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
                }

                .development-title {
                    font-size: 1.5rem;
                }

                .development-subtitle {
                    font-size: 1rem;
                }
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="development-card">
            <div class="development-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-hammer"></i>
            </div>

            <h1 class="development-title">開発中です！</h1>

            <p class="development-subtitle">
                このレッスンは現在開発中です。<br>
                もうしばらくお待ちください！
            </p>

            <div class="progress-indicator">
                <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                <div class="progress-text">開発進捗: 60%</div>
            </div>

            <p class="development-description">
                私たちは日々、より良い学習体験を提供するために<br>
                コンテンツの開発に取り組んでいます。<br>
                完成次第、お知らせいたします！
            </p>

            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="back-button">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i>
                戻る
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>